snippet.title: Blaze (Amiga 500)
snippet.description:
Blaze is a platform game (written in 68000 assembly language) for the Amiga 500. The game was inspired by Sega's Sonic the Hedgehog.

Download ADF here: http://aminet.net/package/game/jump/Blaze
Or here: https://files.catbox.moe/qxgzny.ADF

Note: Tested with Kickstart 1.2
